view.name: Violent Crime & Property Crime Statewide Totals: 2006 to Present
view.attribution: Governor's Office of Crime, Prevention, Youth, and Victim Services (GOCPYVS)
view.description: This dataset shows Maryland crime versus all other states. The data are provided are the Maryland Statistical Analysis Center (MSAC), within the Governor's Office of Crime Control and Prevention (GOCCP). MSAC, in turn, receives these data from the FBI's annual Uniform Crime Reports.
